details: The University of Dhaka is a public research university located in Shahbag, Dhaka, Bangladesh. It is the oldest university in Bangladesh and one of the most prestigious universities in Asia

Independent University, Bangladesh or IUB is a private university in Bangladesh. It is located in Bashundhara Residential Area of Dhaka, Bangladesh. It was established in 1993 under the Private University Act, 1992. IUB has 10,000 students, 11,556 alumni, and 401 faculty members.

North South University is a private research university in Dhaka, Bangladesh. It was established in 1992 by the Foundation for Promotion of Education and Research, a charitable, non-profit, non-commercial and non-political organization
